    <svcproc svcproctype="adjust" graphiccount="0">
        <title>ADJUSTMENT</title>
        <para>On all of the Hendrickson (walking beam) suspensions, alignment is controlled by the locations of the
            frame brackets, and the locations of the beam hangers on the axles.
        </para>
        <para>For the specifics of chassis alignment, refer to GROUP 03-SUSPENSION ALIGNMENT section in the CTS-5000
            Master Service Manual.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
